    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive! She\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014runs like a dream and has clearly been well-loved over the years. You might find a tiny bit of character here and there, but she\u2019s reliable, clean, and ready for all your upcoming road trips. Seriously, you're going to love how smooth this handles! Come take her for a spin!",
