    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine. This naturally aspirated powerplant utilizes six individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS variable valve timing system to deliver 333 hp with a linear power band. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been performed, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing service. The suspension retains its factory-spec handling characteristics with crisp turn-in and minimal body roll. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical synchronization and chassis rigidity remain excellent, making this a quintessential driver-focused example.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
