    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my awesome car. It\u2019s been a fantastic daily driver for me\u2014super reliable and still looks great inside and out! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left for all your upcoming adventures. I've taken good care of it, and I'm sure you'll love how it handles. Drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin or have any questions at all. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six, delivering 333hp with a 8,000 RPM redline. This example maintains its mechanical integrity with a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement\u2014critical for the chassis longevity of this platform. The individual throttle bodies provide instantaneous throttle response, while the suspension remains taut, preserving the communicative steering rack that defines this era. While showing minor cosmetic signs of use consistent with its age, the powertrain remains robust and the rod bearings have been addressed. A high-revving, naturally aspirated icon ready for the apex.",
